node.text:
A closer look at the Astronomia Tourbillon Dragon by @jacobandco 🐉

Firstly we have the mystical dragon which represents strength and power, glory and good fortune.

The process to create this detailed creature takes over 6 months of sourcing the material, creating a 3-D plan, engraving, polishing and ensuring that there is no imperfections.

The watch displays unmatchable craftsmanship and it’s amazing to be able to show you this. Thanks again to @jacobandco for the opportunity.

#millionairesurroundings #jacobandco #rosegold #watch #watches #watchcollector #watchesofinstagram #watchaddict #watchgeek #luxurywatch

node.text:
@jacobandco x @alecmonopoly Astronomia 💰

To celebrate the unique partnership between Jacob & Co and Alec, the pair have launched this exclusive timepiece costing $600,000 and limited to 9 pieces.

The colourful animated watch has a black sky layer base housed in an 18K rose gold case with a curved sapphire crystal dome and four sapphire crystal windows on the side that provide a full view of the artistic and mechanical creations inside.

By: @jacobandco & @alecmonopoly

#jacobandco #watch #watches #watchcollector #watchesofinstagram #watchaddict #watchlover #alecmonopoly #artisanmade #millionairesurroundings

node.text:
@jacobandco Oil Pump finished in white gold #millionairesurroundings

The movements in themselves are incredible feats of watchmaking to the highest of standards. Many of Jacob Arabo’s clients in the oil industry have been requesting he produce something unique for them, and this is the result 😍

The pusher at two o'clock starts the two derricks moving, pumping up and down. Rather than stuffy jaquemarts or something classic, the Oil Pump modernizes the automaton with two oil derricks that move in unison. Depressing the pusher charges the power reserve for the automaton and sets them into action.

What do you think of the movements featured in this beautiful watch?

By: @jacobandco

#jacobandco #watch #watchesofinstagram #watches #watchcollector #limitededition #oil #whitegold #jewelry #custommade
